snippet: More than 500 small earthquakes struck a volcanic region in central California on Thursday and Friday, posing no immediate risk, federal environmental officials said....

headline.print_headline: Hundreds of Small Earthquakes Hit Central California
headline.main: Hundreds of Small Earthquakes Hit Central California

lead_paragraph: More than 500 small earthquakes struck a volcanic region in central California on Thursday and Friday, posing no immediate risk, federal environmental officials said.
